Camp KQ is back this year! National mixer tournament designed for players to have fun while raising money for charity and enjoy the PNW.

Resource sheet: 
https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ngbupHudsfEvk63FJk9wxPcykyhxkyjos36jc70xVJY/edit?usp=drive_link

Teams will be assigned SATURDAY morning of the tournament (so you can't cheat).
tournament.registration_message: If you want a t-shirt ($20) please fill out registration BEFORE 11:59pm 7/11/2024.
